@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Its you that matters!";
}

<div class="row" style="text-align:center;">
    <div class="col-offset-1">
        <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="item active">
                    <img src="~/Content/bridge.jpg" data-src="~/Content/bridge.jpg" alt="ThinkBridge Software Careers">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="carousel-caption">
                            <h1 class="text-muted">Think Bridge.</h1>
                            <p class="label label-success">Explore. Learn. Think. Create. Collaborate. Live.</p>
                            <p class="lead text-muted">We help build careers in Software.</p>                            
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="alert alert-info">
        <p>We have an idea. What if we guided the motivated, logical, & analytical minds to be world class software people? What if one were exposed to live systems from day one? 
        What if they were made to communicate & collaborate from the get go? What if we incorporate a culture that treats each other well, aims for bigger better things, 
        learns by doing, cooperates with empathy, nurtures and grows talent and abilities, celebrates successes & embrace failures, is open minded &amp; curious? 
        What if we teach them to live to create, to embrace change and take calculated risks? @Html.ActionLink("Read more >>", "About", "Home")</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="alert alert-success" style="text-align:center;">
        <p>@Html.ActionLink("Now accepting inquiries for Jan 2014", "Contact", "Home")</p>
    </div>
</div>
